      "source": [
        "# 🔍 鋼板缺陷分析：初步探索\n",
        "## 第一階段：分析之旅啟程 - 探索Other_Faults的奧秘\n",
        "\n",
        "**作者**: Yu-Ching, Chou | 品保工程師\n",
        "**日期**: 2025-07-28  \n",
        "**目標**: 了解Other_Faults的本質 - 最大的未識別缺陷類別  \n",
        "\n",
        "---\n",
        "\n",
        "## 🎯 專案背景\n",
        "\n",
        "身為品保工程師，我一直對鋼材缺陷分析深感興趣。當我發現這個"UCI Machine Learning dataset on steel plate faults"時，我立刻注意到一個狀況：\n",
        "\n",
        "**Other_Faults - 佔所有缺陷的34.7%！**\n",
        "\n",
        "這意味著超過三分之一的缺陷無法正確辨識。從品質管理的角度來看，這既是重大挑戰，也是改善的機會。\n",
        "\n",
        "## 🤔 初步問題\n",
        "\n",
        "- 是什麼讓Other_Faults與已知缺陷類型不同？\n",
        "- 是否存在隱藏的模式可以幫助我們理解這些「未知」缺陷？\n",
        "- 我們能否開發更好的分類方法來降低這個34.7%的不確定性？\n",
        "- 解決這個分類問題會帶來什麼樣的商業影響？\n",
        "\n",
        "## 💡 初步假設\n",
        "\n",
        "基於我在品質管理方面的經驗，我假設Other_Faults可能與特定的製造條件有關，特別是**鋼板厚度**。較厚的鋼板通常需要不同的製程參數，導致產生特殊缺陷模式，因而較難分類。\n",
        "\n",
        "讓我們開始探索..."
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "metadata": {},
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "# 匯入必要的函式庫\n",
        "import pandas as pd\n",
        "import numpy as np\n",
        "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
        "import seaborn as sns\n",
        "from ucimlrepo import fetch_ucirepo\n",
        "import warnings\n",
        "warnings.filterwarnings('ignore')\n",
        "\n",
        "# 設定專業視覺化樣式\n",
        "plt.style.use('seaborn-v0_8')\n",
        "sns.set_palette(\"husl\")\n",
        "\n",
        "# 確保結果可重現\n",
        "np.random.seed(42)\n",
        "\n",
        "print(\"✅ 環境設定完成！\")\n",
        "print(\"🔍 準備探索Other_Faults的奧秘...\")"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "## 📊 資料載入與初步觀察\n",
        "\n",
        "讓我們載入鋼板缺陷資料集，並初步了解資料結構。"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "metadata": {},
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "# 載入鋼板缺陷資料集\n",
        "print(\"📥 載入UCI鋼板缺陷資料集...\")\n",
        "\n",
        "steel_plates_faults = fetch_ucirepo(id=198)\n",
        "X = steel_plates_faults.data.features \n",
        "y = steel_plates_faults.data.targets\n",
        "\n",
        "# 合併特徵與目標變數以便分析\n",
        "df = pd.concat([X, y], axis=1)\n",
        "\n",
        "print(f\"✅ 資料集載入成功！\")\n",
        "print(f\"📊 資料集維度: {df.shape}\")\n",
        "print(f\"🔧 特徵數量: {len(X.columns)}\")\n",
        "print(f\"🎯 目標變數: {list(y.columns)}\")"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "metadata": {},
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "# 顯示資料集基本資訊\n",
        "print(\"📋 資料集概覽:\")\n",
        "print(\"=\" * 50)\n",
        "df.info()"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "metadata": {},
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "# 顯示前幾列以了解資料結構\n",
        "print(\"👀 資料集前5列:\")\n",
        "print(\"=\" * 50)\n",
        "df.head()"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "## 🎯 缺陷類型分布 - 全貌觀察\n",
        "\n",
        "現在讓我們檢視不同缺陷類型的分布，確認我們對Other_Faults的初步觀察。"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "metadata": {},
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "# 計算缺陷類型統計\n",
        "defect_columns = ['Pastry', 'Z_Scratch', 'K_Scratch', 'Stains', 'Dirtiness', 'Bumps', 'Other_Faults']\n",
        "total_samples = len(df)\n",
        "\n",
        "defect_stats = {}\n",
        "for defect in defect_columns:\n",
        "    count = df[defect].sum()\n",
        "    percentage = (count / total_samples) * 100\n",
        "    defect_stats[defect] = {'count': count, 'percentage': percentage}\n",
        "\n",
        "# 顯示統計結果\n",
        "print(\"📊 缺陷類型分布:\")\n",
        "print(\"=\" * 50)\n",
        "for defect, stats in defect_stats.items():\n",
        "    indicator = \"👑\" if defect == 'Other_Faults' else \"📍\"\n",
        "    # 中文標示\n",
        "    defect_names_zh = {\n",
        "        'Pastry': '糕點狀缺陷',\n",
        "        'Z_Scratch': 'Z型刮痕',\n",
        "        'K_Scratch': 'K型刮痕', \n",
        "        'Stains': '污漬',\n",
        "        'Dirtiness': '髒污',\n",
        "        'Bumps': '凸起',\n",
        "        'Other_Faults': '其他缺陷'\n",
        "    }\n",
        "    zh_name = defect_names_zh.get(defect, defect)\n",
        "    print(f\"{indicator} {zh_name:10s}({defect:12s}): {stats['count']:4d} 樣本 ({stats['percentage']:5.1f}%)\")\n",
        "\n",
        "print(f\"\\n🔍 總樣本數: {total_samples}\")"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "metadata": {},
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "# 建立缺陷分布視覺化\n",
        "fig, (ax1, ax2) = plt.subplots(1, 2, figsize=(16, 6))\n",
        "\n",
        "# 長條圖\n",
        "defect_names = list(defect_stats.keys())\n",
        "defect_counts = [stats['count'] for stats in defect_stats.values()]\n",
        "defect_percentages = [stats['percentage'] for stats in defect_stats.values()]\n",
        "\n",
        "# 突顯Other_Faults\n",
        "colors = ['red' if defect == 'Other_Faults' else 'lightblue' for defect in defect_names]\n",
        "\n",
        "bars = ax1.bar(defect_names, defect_counts, color=colors)\n",
        "ax1.set_title('鋼板缺陷分布\\n(Other_Faults特別標示)', fontsize=14, fontweight='bold')\n",
        "ax1.set_xlabel('缺陷類型')\n",
        "ax1.set_ylabel('樣本數量')\n",
        "ax1.tick_params(axis='x', rotation=45)\n",
        "\n",
        "# 在長條上加入百分比標籤\n",
        "for bar, percentage in zip(bars, defect_percentages):\n",
        "    height = bar.get_height()\n",
        "    ax1.text(bar.get_x() + bar.get_width()/2., height + 10,\n",
        "             f'{percentage:.1f}%', ha='center', va='bottom', fontweight='bold')\n",
        "\n",
        "# 圓餅圖聚焦主要類別\n",
        "top_categories = [(name, stats['percentage']) for name, stats in defect_stats.items() \n",
        "                  if stats['percentage'] > 5]  # 只顯示 > 5% 的類別\n",
        "other_small = sum([stats['percentage'] for name, stats in defect_stats.items() \n",
        "                   if stats['percentage'] <= 5])\n",
        "\n",
        "pie_labels = [name for name, _ in top_categories]\n",
        "pie_values = [percentage for _, percentage in top_categories]\n",
        "pie_colors = ['red' if label == 'Other_Faults' else 'lightblue' for label in pie_labels]\n",
        "\n",
        "if other_small > 0:\n",
        "    pie_labels.append('其他 (< 5%)')\n",
        "    pie_values.append(other_small)\n",
        "    pie_colors.append('lightgray')\n",
        "\n",
        "wedges, texts, autotexts = ax2.pie(pie_values, labels=pie_labels, colors=pie_colors, \n",
        "                                   autopct='%1.1f%%', startangle=90)\n",
        "ax2.set_title('缺陷類型分布\\n(Other_Faults佔主導地位)', fontsize=14, fontweight='bold')\n",
        "\n",
        "# 讓Other_Faults的百分比加粗\n",
        "for autotext in autotexts:\n",
        "    if 'Other_Faults' in pie_labels[autotexts.index(autotext)]:\n",
        "        autotext.set_fontweight('bold')\n",
        "        autotext.set_fontsize(12)\n",
        "\n",
        "plt.tight_layout()\n",
        "plt.show()\n",
        "\n",
        "print(\"\\n🎯 關鍵觀察:\")\n",
        "other_faults_pct = defect_stats['Other_Faults']['percentage']\n",
        "print(f\"   Other_Faults佔所有缺陷的 {other_faults_pct:.1f}% - 是最大的類別！\")\n",
        "print(f\"   這意味著有 {defect_stats['Other_Faults']['count']} 個樣本目前無法分類。\")"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "## 🔍 初步假設驗證：厚度分析\n",
        "\n",
        "讓我們測試我的初步假設，即Other_Faults可能與鋼板厚度有關。我們將比較Other_Faults樣本與正常樣本的厚度分布。"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "metadata": {},
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "# 分離Other_Faults樣本與正常樣本\n",
        "other_faults_samples = df[df['Other_Faults'] == 1]\n",
        "normal_samples = df[df['Other_Faults'] == 0]\n",
        "\n",
        "print(f\"📊 樣本分布:\")\n",
        "print(f\"   Other_Faults樣本: {len(other_faults_samples)}\")\n",
        "print(f\"   正常樣本: {len(normal_samples)}\")\n",
        "print(f\"   Other_Faults比例: {len(other_faults_samples)/len(df)*100:.1f}%\")"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "metadata": {},
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "# 比較厚度統計\n",
        "of_thickness = other_faults_samples['Steel_Plate_Thickness']\n",
        "normal_thickness = normal_samples['Steel_Plate_Thickness']\n",
        "\n",
        "print(\"🔧 鋼板厚度比較:\")\n",
        "print(\"=\" * 50)\n",
        "print(f\"Other_Faults厚度:\")\n",
        "print(f\"   平均值: {of_thickness.mean():.1f}mm\")\n",
        "print(f\"   中位數: {of_thickness.median():.1f}mm\")\n",
        "print(f\"   標準差: {of_thickness.std():.1f}mm\")\n",
        "print(f\"   範圍: {of_thickness.min():.1f}mm - {of_thickness.max():.1f}mm\")\n",
        "\n",
        "print(f\"\\n正常樣本厚度:\")\n",
        "print(f\"   平均值: {normal_thickness.mean():.1f}mm\")\n",
        "print(f\"   中位數: {normal_thickness.median():.1f}mm\")\n",
        "print(f\"   標準差: {normal_thickness.std():.1f}mm\")\n",
        "print(f\"   範圍: {normal_thickness.min():.1f}mm - {normal_thickness.max():.1f}mm\")\n",
        "\n",
        "# 計算差異\n",
        "mean_diff = abs(of_thickness.mean() - normal_thickness.mean())\n",
        "mean_diff_pct = (mean_diff / normal_thickness.mean()) * 100\n",
        "\n",
        "print(f\"\\n📈 統計差異:\")\n",
        "print(f\"   平均值差異: {mean_diff:.1f}mm ({mean_diff_pct:.1f}%)\")\n",
        "\n",
        "if mean_diff_pct > 20:\n",
        "    print(f\"   🎯 初步假設似乎獲得驗證！檢測到顯著的厚度差異。\")\n",
        "else:\n",
        "    print(f\"   🤔 初步假設可能需要修正。差異程度為中等。\")"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "## 🔍 關鍵特徵分析\n",
        "\n",
        "讓我們檢視一些關鍵特徵，了解Other_Faults與正常樣本的區別。"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "metadata": {},
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "# 選擇關鍵特徵進行比較\n",
        "key_features = ['Steel_Plate_Thickness', 'Sum_of_Luminosity', 'Pixels_Areas', \n",
        "                'X_Perimeter', 'Y_Perimeter', 'Outside_X_Index']\n",
        "\n",
        "# 特徵中文對照\n",
        "feature_names_zh = {\n",
        "    'Steel_Plate_Thickness': '鋼板厚度',\n",
        "    'Sum_of_Luminosity': '亮度總和',\n",
        "    'Pixels_Areas': '像素面積',\n",
        "    'X_Perimeter': 'X軸周長',\n",
        "    'Y_Perimeter': 'Y軸周長',\n",
        "    'Outside_X_Index': '外部X索引'\n",
        "}\n",
        "\n",
        "print(\"📊 關鍵特徵比較 (Other_Faults vs 正常):\")\n",
        "print(\"=\" * 80)\n",
        "print(f\"{'特徵':<15} {'英文名稱':<20} {'OF平均':<10} {'正常平均':<10} {'差異%':<10}\")\n",
        "print(\"-\" * 80)\n",
        "\n",
        "feature_differences = []\n",
        "for feature in key_features:\n",
        "    of_mean = other_faults_samples[feature].mean()\n",
        "    normal_mean = normal_samples[feature].mean()\n",
        "    diff_pct = abs(of_mean - normal_mean) / normal_mean * 100\n",
        "    \n",
        "    feature_differences.append({\n",
        "        'feature': feature,\n",
        "        'feature_zh': feature_names_zh.get(feature, feature),\n",
        "        'of_mean': of_mean,\n",
        "        'normal_mean': normal_mean,\n",
        "        'diff_pct': diff_pct\n",
        "    })\n",
        "    \n",
        "    zh_name = feature_names_zh.get(feature, feature)\n",
        "    print(f\"{zh_name:<15} {feature:<20} {of_mean:<10.1f} {normal_mean:<10.1f} {diff_pct:<10.1f}%\")\n",
        "\n",
        "# 找出差異最大的特徵\n",
        "feature_differences.sort(key=lambda x: x['diff_pct'], reverse=True)\n",
        "print(f\"\\n🔍 最具區別性的特徵:\")\n",
        "for i, feat in enumerate(feature_differences[:3], 1):\n",
        "    print(f\"   {i}. {feat['feature_zh']} ({feat['feature']}): {feat['diff_pct']:.1f}% 差異\")"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "## 📈 初步結論與下一步\n",
        "\n",
        "基於這次初步探索，讓我總結我們的發現並規劃後續步驟。"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "metadata": {},
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "print(\"📋 初步探索總結\")\n",
        "print(\"=\" * 50)\n",
        "\n",
        "print(f\"\\n🎯 主要發現:\")\n",
        "print(f\"   • Other_Faults確實是最大的缺陷類別，佔 {other_faults_pct:.1f}%\")\n",
        "print(f\"   • {len(other_faults_samples)} 個樣本目前無法分類\")\n",
        "print(f\"   • 厚度假設顯示 {mean_diff_pct:.1f}% 差異 - {'顯著' if mean_diff_pct > 20 else '中等'}\")\n",
        "\n",
        "top_diff_feature = feature_differences[0]\n",
        "print(f\"   • 最具區別性特徵: {top_diff_feature['feature_zh']} ({top_diff_feature['diff_pct']:.1f}% 差異)\")\n",
        "\n",
        "print(f\"\\n🤔 引發的問題:\")\n",
        "print(f\"   • 為什麼Other_Faults具有如此不同的特性？\")\n",
        "print(f\"   • Other_Faults類別內是否存在隱藏的模式？\")\n",
        "print(f\"   • 我們能否開發更好的分類方法？\")\n",
        "\n",
        "print(f\"\\n🚀 下一步計畫:\")\n",
        "print(f\"   1. 深入視覺化分析 - 建立分布圖\")\n",
        "print(f\"   2. 對Other_Faults樣本進行聚類分析\")\n",
        "print(f\"   3. 分析與其他缺陷類型的相關性\")\n",
        "print(f\"   4. 調查這些差異的根本原因\")\n",
        "\n",
        "print(f\"\\n💡 初步假設狀態:\")\n",
        "if mean_diff_pct > 30:\n",
        "    status = \"強力支持\"\n",
        "elif mean_diff_pct > 15:\n",
        "    status = \"部分支持\"\n",
        "else:\n",
        "    status = \"需要修正\"\n",
        "    \n",
        "print(f\"   厚度相關假設: {status}\")\n",
        "print(f\"   但我們需要更深入的分析來了解全貌...\")"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "---\n",
        "\n",
        "## 🎯 第一階段結束\n",
        "\n",
        "這次初步探索確認了Other_Faults確實是個重大挑戰，佔所有缺陷的三分之一以上。我也發現這些樣本與正常樣本具有明顯不同的特性，特別是在厚度和其他關鍵特徵方面。\n",
        "\n",
        "然而，統計平均值有時可能會誤導。在下一個notebook (`02_visual_insights.ipynb`)中，我們將建立詳細的視覺化圖表，更理解真實的分布模式，並檢查我們的統計發現是否經得起視覺化考驗。\n",
